## 🚀 Deployment (Vercel)

1. `git push` to a GitHub repository.
2. Go to [vercel.com](https://vercel.com), create a **New Project**, and import the GitHub repository.
3. Vercel auto-detects Next.js — no special configuration needed.
4. The app will be live at a `.vercel.app` URL within minutes.
5. To link a custom domain from GoDaddy: In Vercel project settings → Domains → add your domain → Vercel provides CNAME/A records → paste them into GoDaddy DNS Management.

